BootstrapPeer, FullPeer, SimplePeer
public abstract class Peer
extends Node

The Peer is an abstract class that extends Node class.

Class Peer permits to send and receive message, add and remove peer descriptor into the list, print log.

Author:
Fabrizio Caramia
